name: BASED RABBIT
description: Hi, I am Rabbit. I am $RABBIT 's pet and he is rich! So I am taking his token and giving it away to all my frens! Join me on the ride of a lifetime. When we look at the moon, people from european countries might think about the legend of The Man in The Moon. But Others from Japan have legend about The Rabbit in The Moon. According to them, The moon is inhabited by a rabbit who always pound Mochi Cakes, Lets go to the moon with the rabbit. Community Takeover, And We Have Strong Community
